{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d65365e7c7","title":"给鼓荣臻“并于橡祥的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f1132ea1e6","index":0,"year":1946,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"d65365e7c7"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f0928fa2a5","type":"paragraph","text":"给鼓荣臻“并于橡祥的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"d65365e7c7"},{"id":"aa64e961c9","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年5月19日）慧，并转橡祥同志关于派机接橡祥赴苏治病，自我方交涉后，彼方考康已久，初则顾虑国际环境，要祥夫妇去外蒙登机，但现在已无此种顾虑决定派机直飞张家口。因此现在只有一个称祥身体能否坐飞机的向题。请橡祥自己决定告我，即可告远方派机来接。我意只要身体勉强可以乘机，以去苏医治为上策。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"d65365e7c7"},{"id":"b8c852d8ef","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"d65365e7c7"},{"id":"c8df8530bf","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十九日E最荣琳，当时任晋察翼军区司令员兼致治委员。王穗祥（1906-1974），安徽泾县人。抗日战争时期曾任中共中央12]最荣琳，当时任晋察翼军区司令员兼致治委员。军委副主腐兼总致治部主任。1946年去苏联治病。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"d65365e7c7"}],"page":{"id":"46b2c0fe92","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"d65365e7c7","start":334,"end":334}}}},"__N_SSG":true}